            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Hadri<lb break="no" n="2"/>anus Antoninus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> Pi<lb break="no" n="3"/>us <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ontifex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>aximus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> XX <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>IIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> amphitheatrum vetus<lb break="no" n="5"/>tate dilapsum denuo fe<lb break="no" n="6"/>cit curante <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> Quinti<lb break="no" n="7"/>liano <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratore</ex></expan> suo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Wiederaufbau erfolgte in Stein (zuvor Holzkonstruktion).</p>
